{"tid":1493430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上台客係無得拒收香港政府(警察)嘅短訊","createTime":"2019-08-21T08:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T08:43:52.000Z","uid":64375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bf635859a6b3a39133e4db1df96180178fd4c90e","tid":1493430,"uid":64375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/21/9DfPHT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F21%2F9DfPHT.png&h=140c8315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前問左幾個台，3HK覆左我，登記左拒收訊息登記冊都會照樣收到<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190819/20751691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190819%2F20751691&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9onXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=4f7f66d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190819%2F20751691&h=e9ae8c32\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190819/20751691</a><br />\n<br />\n警方回覆《蘋果》查詢時證實短訊由警方發放，指四個主要流動網絡營辦商按既定程序，收到通訊事務管理局要求後代警方向其註冊用戶發出流動電話短訊，提醒市民在大型公眾活動其間提高警覺，但預繳電話卡的用戶及已登記「拒收訊息登記冊」的用戶不會收到短訊。"}]}